  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Play time per run: 20–30 min</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">All stages cleared: 4+ hours + Endless mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/8a684aba9f7850e77e7c7bffd3abb7c0.poster.avif?t=1774008948\" width=898 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/8a684aba9f7850e77e7c7bffd3abb7c0.webm?t=1774008948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/8a684aba9f7850e77e7c7bffd3abb7c0.mp4?t=1774008948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>A medieval civilization is sealed inside every card—locked away by alchemy.  <br>Draw each turn, place your buildings, and watch your colony take shape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/28960c86e11ad5d12ac7fc3aa8e41b53.poster.avif?t=1774008948\" width=1170 height=566 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/28960c86e11ad5d12ac7fc3aa8e41b53.webm?t=1774008948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/28960c86e11ad5d12ac7fc3aa8e41b53.mp4?t=1774008948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Deckbuilding is the heart of the game.  <br>Remove what you don’t need, and choose what you’ll take into this run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/8c88972c2072599b68a941a89451bd7d.avif?t=1774008948\" width=1200 height=230 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/33d9839960e735993e5835fe6077b3a2.poster.avif?t=1774008948\" width=952 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/33d9839960e735993e5835fe6077b3a2.webm?t=1774008948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/33d9839960e735993e5835fe6077b3a2.mp4?t=1774008948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>But as the days pass, they fight back. <br>Penalty cards appear to sabotage your run, destroying or transforming your towers and keeping the pressure on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/8c88972c2072599b68a941a89451bd7d.avif?t=1774008948\" width=1200 height=230 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Survive the relentless waves of threats—and build an empire of your own!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/62c0a5162250d79aef0407ca2b61f01e.avif?t=1774008948\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/8c88972c2072599b68a941a89451bd7d.avif?t=1774008948\" width=1200 height=230 /></span></p>",
