move what you don’t need, and choose what you’ll take into this run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/8c88972c2072599b68a941a89451bd7d.avif?t=1774008948\" width=1200 height=230 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/33d9839960e735993e5835fe6077b3a2.poster.avif?t=1774008948\" width=952 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/33d9839960e735993e5835fe6077b3a2.webm?t=1774008948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/33d9839960e735993e5835fe6077b3a2.mp4?t=1774008948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>But as the days pass, they fight back. <br>Penalty cards appear to sabotage your run, destroying or transforming your towers and keeping the pressure on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/8c88972c2072599b68a941a89451bd7d.avif?t=1774008948\" width=1200 height=230 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Survive the relentless waves of threats—and build an empire of your own!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236830/extras/62c0a5162250d79aef0407ca2b61f01e.avif?t=1774008948\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass